                <mxCell id="X_p-jio8kUHtuNGoBsOz-0" value="GLOBAL&lt;div&gt;Questions for clients:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;- 2 quotes-creation workflows:&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;+ Do you want a user to create a quote and then u can confirm it and the system will automatically send the confirmation email to user.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;+ Or Do you want a user to request a quote and then there is an email sent to user to let them know that their requested has been sent and they will get the confirmation via email with 24 hours. Once they get it they have 48 hours to confirm the quote.&lt;/div&gt;" style="shape=note;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;backgroundOutline=1;fontColor=#000000;darkOpacity=0.05;fillColor=#FFF9B2;strokeColor=none;fillStyle=solid;direction=west;gradientDirection=north;gradientColor=#FFF2A1;shadow=1;size=20;pointerEvents=1;" parent="WIyWlLk6GJQsqaUBKTNV-1" vertex="1">
